item.title: CVE-2020-5855|2024-08-04T08:39:25.885Z -- f5 -- edge%20client%20for%20windows
item.description: When the Windows Logon Integration feature is configured for all versions of BIG-IP Edge Client for Windows, unauthorized users who have physical access to an authorized user's machine can get shell access under unprivileged user.
